00:18:25,655 --> 00:18:28,357
who never had a nice word
to say about Finn Hudson,

375
00:18:28,391 --> 00:18:30,493
so don't you dare think
for a second

376
00:18:30,527 --> 00:18:31,994
that he didn't hate you, too!

377
00:18:32,028 --> 00:18:35,531
If I were you, I would choose my
next few words very carefully.

378
00:18:35,565 --> 00:18:37,833
What are you gonna do?
You gonna expel me?

379
00:18:37,868 --> 00:18:38,968
You get the hell
out of my office!

