00:18:39,002 --> 00:18:40,703
How about you make me get
the hell out of your office?

381
00:18:40,737 --> 00:18:42,705
Donna, call the police.
Donna, you pick up that phone,

382
00:18:42,739 --> 00:18:44,907
and I swear to God,
I will shove my foot so far...

383
00:18:44,941 --> 00:18:47,009
That's assault!
No, this is assault!

