386
00:18:56,353 --> 00:18:57,520
Tina, I'm really glad that

387
00:18:57,554 --> 00:18:59,922
you took the time
to come talk to me today.

388
00:18:59,956 --> 00:19:01,857
I know a lot of young people

389
00:19:01,892 --> 00:19:03,859
have trouble expressing
feelings of sadness.

390
00:19:03,894 --> 00:19:06,862
I just don't know how
much longer I can do this.

391
00:19:06,897 --> 00:19:08,197
Do what?

392
00:19:08,231 --> 00:19:11,200
I just don't know how much
longer I can wear black.

393
00:19:11,234 --> 00:19:14,870
I feel like this look is
so Tina two years ago.

394
00:19:14,905 --> 00:19:17,373
And I spent so much time
transitioning away from goth,

395
00:19:17,407 --> 00:19:20,142
and look at me... it's, like,
I'm back in that look.

