416
00:20:08,758 --> 00:20:10,726
What are you saying, that...

417
00:20:10,760 --> 00:20:12,561
that-that I don't feel anything?
No, that's

418
00:20:12,596 --> 00:20:13,996
not what... Of course I
feel something, Emma.

419
00:20:14,030 --> 00:20:16,498
I-I feel...

