00:20:27,711 --> 00:20:28,844
around me are taken care of.

426
00:20:28,879 --> 00:20:30,412
Okay. Okay.

427
00:20:30,447 --> 00:20:32,167
Look, I-I... this... Listen to me.
Listen...

428
00:20:32,182 --> 00:20:33,282
Listen to me; listen.

429
00:20:33,316 --> 00:20:34,750
I love you, okay?

430
00:20:34,784 --> 00:20:37,219
I know. Whatever you feel and
however you want to show it,

431
00:20:37,254 --> 00:20:39,154
that's okay.

